tspan.tspan: Cyberpunk has been my absolute favorite game ever since I
first played it. I love everything about it. In fact, its the only
piece of media that has ever made me cry - the King of
Wands ending of Phantom Liberty, to be precise. Ive always
been drawn to sci-fi and RPGs that give me space to be
creative - to write my own character backstories and then
Modding is another passion of mine, and Cyberpunk offers an
endless array of mods to explore. The game - or CDPR in
general - has truly mastered the art of making players feel
deep emotions, and honestly, I kind of enjoy that sadness.
Plus, the fact that its a Polish game makes it even more
Right now, Im working on my Vs character sheet. Its taking
some time because I want every detail to feel special.
Writing the story is the most time-consuming part, especially
since finding the energy and free time isnt always easy.
Once its finished, Ill post it on my private website.
